745
00:37:44.179 --> 00:37:46.515
But if you do need time away

746
00:37:46.598 --> 00:37:48.517
to think

747
00:37:48.600 --> 00:37:50.894
and if you trust me...

748
00:37:52.312 --> 00:37:54.648
