meet me up on the roof?"

753
00:38:30.684 --> 00:38:33.186
Billy fucking McBride.

754
00:39:20.776 --> 00:39:22.110
Hey. miss!

755
00:39:23.612 --> 00:39:25.280
Hey!

756
00:39:25.363 --> 00:39:26.406
